The following information applies to The Blaster Blade: Iron Heart game.
Lufick built The Blaster Blade: Iron Heart game as a Freemium app. This SERVICE is provided by Lufick and is intended for use as is. This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our Service.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The Personal Information that we collect or may collect is used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
